title: Olympic swimmer Grant Hackett reportedly in police custody on Gold Coast - ABC News (Australian Broadcasting Corporation)
text:
Olympic swimmer Grant Hackett reportedly in police custody on Gold Coast Posted February 15, 2017 14:39:46 
Former champion swimmer Grant Hackett has reportedly been taken into police custody on Queensland's Gold Coast. 
Police said they were called to a disturbance at Hackett's house earlier. 
The 36-year-old has been taken to the Southport watch house. 
No other details are known at this stage. 
More to come.
